  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556960/extras/e45389a6c4906ae6a4e14361824083fb.poster.avif?t=1734003456\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556960/extras/e45389a6c4906ae6a4e14361824083fb.webm?t=1734003456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556960/extras/e45389a6c4906ae6a4e14361824083fb.mp4?t=1734003456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Have you ever wanted to see what Russia would look like if all the stereotypes about it were true? <br><br>Red Frozen is a game that embodies all the stereotypes about Russia and even a little more.<br>Only here you can ask a neighbor for a Kalashnikov assault rifle, go hunting with him and launch an intercontinental ballistic missile.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556960/extras/7bbd28c8d3d553444ef324903898a919.avif?t=1734003456\" width=614 height=182 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Maximum Of Cranberries !!!<br></li><li> Unique style of stereotypes and anecdotes about Russia;<br></li><li> Nice graphics;<br></li><li> Sophisticated shooting mechanics;<br></li><li> Lots of Easter eggs;<br></li><li> Possibility to play the balalaika![/]<br><br>The action takes place in the village \"Vatnikovo\". A simple Russian peasant, Ivan, is being nailed by his wife, because by the age of 40 he had not tamed a bear. Help him in this difficult case!<br>Drink vodka, play a balalaika and tame a real Russian bear!<br><br>Even in summer it is cold enough in Russia, so do not forget to put on a quilted jacket and start a nuclear reactor so as not to freeze!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556960/extras/2ba6b583b3a6db12d8dfb99ec4dce6ab.avif?t=1734003456\" width=614 height=182 /></span><br>The game is developed by 1.5 people (if you count by man-hours), or 3.25 (if you count by weight).</li></ul>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556960/extras/e45389a6c4906ae6a4e14361824083fb.poster.avif?t=1734003456\" width=620 height=340 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556960/extras/e45389a6c4906ae6a4e14361824083fb.webm?t=1734003456\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556960/extras/e45389a6c4906ae6a4e14361824083fb.mp4?t=1734003456\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Have you ever wanted to see what Russia would look like if all the stereotypes about it were true? <br><br>Red Frozen is a game that embodies all the stereotypes about Russia and even a little more.<br>Only here you can ask a neighbor for a Kalashnikov assault rifle, go hunting with him and launch an intercontinental ballistic missile.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556960/extras/7bbd28c8d3d553444ef324903898a919.avif?t=1734003456\" width=614 height=182 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Maximum Of Cranberries !!!<br></li><li> Unique style of stereotypes and anecdotes about Russia;<br></li><li> Nice graphics;<br></li><li> Sophisticated shooting mechanics;<br></li><li> Lots of Easter eggs;<br></li><li> Possibility to play the balalaika![/]<br><br>The action takes place in the village \"Vatnikovo\". A simple Russian peasant, Ivan, is being nailed by his wife, because by the age of 40 he had not tamed a bear. Help him in this difficult case!<br>Drink vodka, play a balalaika and tame a real Russian bear!<br><br>Even in summer it is cold enough in Russia, so do not forget to put on a quilted jacket and start a nuclear reactor so as not to freeze!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1556960/extras/2ba6b583b3a6db12d8dfb99ec4dce6ab.avif?t=1734003456\" width=614 height=182 /></span><br>The game is developed by 1.5 people (if you count by man-hours), or 3.25 (if you count by weight).</li></ul>",
